### Available Workflows

#### Preproduction
- `brainstorming` - Explore ideas freely
- `game-brief` - Define game vision

#### Design
- `gdd` - Complete game design document
- `narrative` - Story and characters
- `art-direction` - Visual style guide

#### Technical
- `game-architecture` - Technical architecture
- `project-context` - Project context document

#### Production
- `sprint-planning` - Plan development sprints
- `dev-story` - Implement user stories
- `code-review` - Code review workflow

### Starting Workflows

